{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water in mixing bowl and bring to a boil <nobr>5 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Set Varoma dish in position, add peppers, close Varoma and steam <nobr>12-14 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr> or until peppers are tender but still have a slight crunch. Remove Varoma, transfer peppers to a serving bowl or jar and empty mixing bowl.","Place extra virgin olive oil, white wine vinegar, cumin and salt in mixing bowl and mix <nobr>20 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>. Pour dressing over peppers, combine thoroughly using spatula and allow to cool and marinate for at least 30 minutes. Season to taste and serve as a side dish at room temperature or chilled."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["500 g water","700 g mixed peppers (e.g. red, green, yellow, orange) cut in pieces or strips","100 g extra virgin olive oil","35 g white wine vinegar","1 tsp ground cumin","3 pinches salt"]}],"id":"r150923","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-C5FhP8o8sps\/XZWZMA3G7iI\/AAAAAAAAeJE\/BZzC0oBHpEUyJ5EIGTYjQg1M9ePaCMY3QCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_WFoztc7hKnkTUMQY.png","title":"Marinated Peppers","publishedAt":"2017-06-01T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"1.5 g","fat":"9 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"6 g","calories":"490 kJ \/ 117 kcal"},"usefulItems":"jar, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["<i>As a side dish, these marinated peppers add a fresh and colourful note to your meal. They are particularly welcome on a buffet table, and stored in an airtight, sterilised jar they make an attractive homemade gift.<\/i>","Serve with fish or grilled meat.<br>- Allow to marinate longer to intensify the flavour.<br>- Peppers can be stored in a sterilised jar in the fridge for up to one week.","<strong>Mediterranean Style Peppers:<\/strong> In <nobr>step 2,<\/nobr> after steaming the peppers, add anchovies, capers, oregano and black olives (to taste) to the serving bowl."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","55m","6 portions"]}